lead_paragraph: South Africa captain AB De Villiers has been ruled out of the one-day international and test series against Australia after failing to recover from an elbow injury, Cricket South Africa said on Tuesday.

headline.print_headline: South Africa's De Villiers to Miss Australia Series
headline.main: South Africa's De Villiers to Miss Australia Series
